Some police departments use their own series of codes that aren&#39;t published
anywhere and aren&#39;t used by others. And the &quot;signal&quot; seven may have a
different meaning than the &quot;code&quot; seven. It could be so widely used that the
police officers all understand what is meant by the context.
As I said, in the case of ICS/NIMS systems, the use of any of these is
discouraged.

Zack


